sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Telegram)
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant US as User Service
    participant PS as Practice Service
    participant QS as Quiz Service
    participant BS as Booking Service
    participant PYS as Payment Service
    participant NS as Notification Service
    participant CS as Calendar Service
    
    Note over U,CS: Scenario: User books a practice
    
    U->>GW: GET /practices?date=2025-12-27
    GW->>US: Validate Telegram auth
    US-->>GW: ✓ User authenticated
    GW->>PS: Get practices for date
    PS-->>GW: List of practices
    GW-->>U: Display practices
    
    U->>GW: GET /practices/{practice_id}
    GW->>PS: Get practice details
    PS->>QS: Get pre-practice quiz
    QS-->>PS: Quiz questions
    PS-->>GW: Practice + Quiz
    GW-->>U: Show details
    
    U->>GW: POST /bookings (practice_id)
    GW->>US: Validate user
    US-->>GW: ✓ User valid
    
    GW->>BS: Create booking
    BS->>PS: Check availability
    PS-->>BS: Available (5/20 slots)
    
    alt Practice requires payment
        BS->>PYS: Check subscription
        PYS-->>BS: Active subscription ✓
    end
    
    BS->>PS: Increment participants
    PS-->>BS: Updated
    
    BS-->>GW: Booking created (status: confirmed)
    GW-->>U: Booking confirmed
    
    BS->>NS: Create notification (booking_confirmed)
    NS->>U: Send Telegram message
    
    BS->>CS: Schedule reminders
    CS-->>BS: Reminders scheduled (24h, 1h, 10min)
    
    Note over U,CS: 24 hours before practice
    
    CS->>NS: Trigger 24h reminder
    NS->>QS: Get pre-practice quiz
    QS-->>NS: Quiz link
    NS->>U: "Practice tomorrow! Fill quiz: [link]"
    
    Note over U,CS: User fills pre-practice quiz
    
    U->>GW: POST /quizzes/{quiz_id}/responses
    GW->>QS: Submit response
    QS->>STS: Send to State Service
    QS-->>GW: Response saved
    GW-->>U: Thank you!
